casebody.data:
Marcel W. WILLIAMS
v.
KELLEY, Dir., AR DOC, et al. No. 16-8815 (16A1029). Supreme Court of the United States April 24, 2017.

The application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice Alito and by him referred to the Court is denied. The petition for a writ of certiorari is denied.

Justice SOTOMAYOR, dissenting from the denial of the application for stay and the denial of certiorari.

I dissent for the reasons set out in McGehee v. Hutchinson , 581 U.S. ----, --- S.Ct. ----, --- L.Ed.2d ----, 2017 WL 1414915 (2017) (Sotomayor, J., dissenting).
